earnestly in the slave-girl\'92s face, and murmured the word \
\'93Ty due!\'94 The face of Sophronia lighted up as with a sunbeam, \
and she joyfully re-echoed the wordtwice. \'91The Greek clasped \
her hand warmly, and with a parting salutation in his own \
tongue, went on his way. \
