signification of the word /x\'e9u:. \'91A fish, Camilla,\'94 was the \
simple answer ; and Camilla was more puzzled than ever. \'93A \
fish !\'94 what was there in the mere word \'93fish\'94 to call up such \
a joyous expression on the countenances of the two Greeks? \
