face expressed her annoyance quite as clearly asher rather profane \
exclamation in reply. One of the slaves, startled by her sudden \
speech, or by the fact that his fellow-slave as he passed him \
bestowed on him a sharp pinch, let the turbot fall, and Aurelia, \
raising herself from her couch, rewarded him by a box on the ear \
