his pallium, and quitted the house. Aurelia, who had a some- \
what non-Roman weakness for an early breakfast, summoned \
Libia, and bade her bring into the peristyle a basin of polenta, \
a jug of milk, and some of the hot breakfast-cakes which were \
being cried in the streets, and left at the doors of regular custo- \
mers. On these cakes the bakers were accustomed to stamp \
their names with a metal die, thus practising the art of printing \
